Sentencas: In this study, catalytic current collecting layer (CCCL) was added to thin-film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O1-delta (LSCF) cathode for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells to improve both in-plane resistance and catalytic activity.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: N, Pd, Cu, Ag, and Au were applied as CCCL of thin-film LSCF cathode.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: The thickness of the CCCL was varied from 100 nm to 300 nm.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: These CCCLs were deposited by sputtering on PLD-deposited LSCF cathode on a single-crystalline YSZ pellet.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: By adding the CCCLs, the maximum power density improved compared to the bare LSCF cathode cells.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: It was found that N, Pd, and Ag CCCLs improved both ohmic and faradaic impedance as the CCCLs' thickness increased.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: However, for Cu CCCL, the thicker layer did not enhance the performance.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: The N CCCL cell showed the highest peak power density with the thickest layer.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: However, Au exhibited a noteworthy performance despite thinner thickness compared to all other materials.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: It turned out electronic conductivity of raw materials is dominant for the performance enhancement.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance was investigated through polarization curves and Nyquist plots.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: Also, long-term stabilities were measured with potentiostat mode.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: The microstructure of CCCLs was investigated through FIB-SEM and FE-SEM.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode

Sentencas: Crystal structures of CCCL-added LSCF were studied through XRD.
Titulo: Electrochemical study on the effect of catalytic current collecting layer on thin film La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ (LSCF) cathode
